WEBVTT

01:40.851 --> 01:44.691
<b><i>It's spring, so I thought I could get away 
with no jacket for a smoke run,</i></b>

01:44.691 --> 01:47.231
<b><i>but it still gets 
pretty chilly at night, huh?</i></b>

01:48.651 --> 01:51.321
<b><i>I'll have a smoke somewhere 
before I go home.</i></b>

01:54.201 --> 01:57.741
<b>Yamada-chan, I'll take over.</b>

01:57.741 --> 01:59.121
<b>Cheers.</b>

02:04.081 --> 02:06.501
<b><i>He didn't show up tonight.</i></b>

02:06.501 --> 02:09.671
<b><i>Overtime? Is he stuck 
at work until morning?</i></b>

02:09.671 --> 02:11.961
<b>Oh, and one more thing.</b>

02:11.961 --> 02:12.841
<b>Yes?</b>

02:13.221 --> 02:17.051
<b>The manager wants to speak 
with you before you leave.</b>

02:25.101 --> 02:26.351
<b>Tayama-san, good ev—</b>

02:26.351 --> 02:29.231
<b>pissssssed</b>

02:29.271 --> 02:31.731
<b>She's in a foul mood...</b>

02:29.521 --> 02:30.941
<b><i>Yikes.</i></b>

02:37.621 --> 02:39.411
<b>Hey, if it ain't Sasaki-san.</b>

02:39.411 --> 02:40.451
<b>Hey.</b>

02:40.451 --> 02:43.041
<b>Don't just stand there. Come take a seat.</b>

02:43.041 --> 02:44.041
<b>Thanks.</b>

02:49.501 --> 02:50.671
<b>Tayama-san, did something—</b>

02:50.671 --> 02:53.051
<b>Were you off work today?</b>

02:53.051 --> 02:53.511
<b>Huh?</b>

02:54.421 --> 02:56.091
<b>Oh, yeah, for once.</b>

02:57.801 --> 03:00.431
<b>That response just screams sweatshop.</b>

03:07.441 --> 03:09.361
<b>Glad you got a day off.</b>

03:25.411 --> 03:28.421
<b>Cold</b>

03:25.411 --> 03:28.421
<b>Hot</b>

03:25.411 --> 03:28.421
<b>Hot</b>

03:28.421 --> 03:29.961
<b>Aren't you gonna smoke?</b>

03:29.961 --> 03:32.291
<b>It's cold out, so I'm getting a drink.</b>

03:32.751 --> 03:34.421
<b>Join me.</b>

03:37.511 --> 03:39.261
<b>When you're feeling down,</b>

03:39.261 --> 03:43.971
<b>a hot drink helps more than 
cigarettes and alcohol, you know?</b>

03:50.351 --> 03:53.441
<b>I got a complaint 
for the first time in ages.</b>

03:53.691 --> 03:56.281
<b>"I've always thought 
her customer service was flawless,</b>

03:56.281 --> 03:59.281
<b>but I smelled cigarette smoke 
on her today. I expected better."</b>

03:59.781 --> 04:04.331
<b>The boss told me not to take it to heart, 
'cuz it's just unreasonable whining.</b>

04:10.791 --> 04:12.461
<b>But when this crap happens,</b>

04:12.961 --> 04:14.841
<b>everything starts to feel so stupid.</b>

04:20.881 --> 04:22.301
<b>That's sad.</b>

04:23.301 --> 04:28.981
<b>I don't get feeling betrayed by somebody 
as soon as you see a new side to them.</b>

04:29.851 --> 04:31.651
<b>They're both the same person, you know?</b>

04:35.151 --> 04:38.071
<b>Oh, but I'm not one to talk.</b>

04:38.071 --> 04:42.571
<b>I don't even know what section you work.</b>

04:46.291 --> 04:50.621
<b>S-Sorry, I stepped out dressed 
too lightly, and I keep sneezing.</b>

04:56.501 --> 04:58.881
<b>Tayama-san? What are you doing?!</b>

05:03.641 --> 05:04.891
<b>You can borrow that for tonight.</b>

05:08.851 --> 05:13.981
<b>It's warm. Thank you, Tayama-san.</b>

05:28.081 --> 05:29.371
<b>No, thank you.</b>

05:39.421 --> 05:42.471
<b>Also, I'm sorry, but I have to say this.</b>

05:43.091 --> 05:45.091
<b>I don't drink coffee.</b>

05:45.931 --> 05:48.431
<b>You look surprised.</b>

05:48.431 --> 05:50.561
<b>That's not why.</b>

05:51.061 --> 05:53.101
<b>I actually don't drink it either.</b>

05:54.101 --> 05:56.691
<b>Let's just get another drink, huh?</b>

05:56.691 --> 05:59.271
<b>Big Bad Bull for me, then.</b>

06:06.491 --> 06:08.831
<b><i>Lovely weather today.</i></b>

06:09.621 --> 06:12.791
<b><i>Nothing feels better 
than the warm sunlight in spring.</i></b>

06:13.331 --> 06:15.871
<b><i>It warms the tired cockles 
of my heart and soul.</i></b>

06:17.711 --> 06:21.341
<b><i>Especially after a client chewed me out.</i></b>

06:18.211 --> 06:21.631
<b>I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!</b>

06:18.381 --> 06:19.291
<b>I'm so sorry</b>

06:19.631 --> 06:20.591
<b>I'm so sorry</b>

06:21.131 --> 06:22.091
<b>I'm so sorry</b>

06:21.631 --> 06:23.841
<b>I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!</b>

06:22.631 --> 06:23.591
<b>I'm so sorry</b>

06:24.341 --> 06:26.841
<b><i>I need to get back to work.</i></b>

06:26.841 --> 06:30.351
<b><i>Guess I'll buy some lunch 
at Super S on the way back.</i></b>

06:32.681 --> 06:35.851
<b><i>Tayama-san probably works 
the night shift, right?</i></b>

06:38.611 --> 06:41.151
<b><i>I doubt she'd be here right now...</i></b>

06:45.991 --> 06:47.741
<b>Tayama-san...</b>

06:48.991 --> 06:49.991
<b>What?!</b>

06:49.991 --> 06:52.491
<b>Y-Y-Yamada-san?!</b>

06:52.491 --> 06:54.001
<b>Hello!</b>

06:54.291 --> 06:56.711
<b>Wh-What are you doing here?</b>

06:56.711 --> 07:00.001
<b>Wait, you work during the day, too?</b>

07:00.291 --> 07:02.921
<b>Sasaki-san, calm down, will you?</b>

07:02.921 --> 07:05.261
<b>Oh, s-sorry about that.</b>

07:05.551 --> 07:10.221
<b>I mostly do night shifts, 
but I'm filling in for someone today.</b>

07:10.221 --> 07:12.011
<b>And I'm here because...</b>

07:12.391 --> 07:14.271
<b>Calm down... Calm down.</b>

07:18.601 --> 07:21.151
<b>It's the only spot here 
with a vending machine.</b>

07:21.151 --> 07:23.401
<b>Oh, is that so.</b>

07:23.401 --> 07:25.531
<b>Did you get off work early?</b>

07:25.531 --> 07:29.031
<b>No, I was on my way back,</b>

07:29.031 --> 07:31.871
<b>but if Tayama-san was here, 
I thought I could join her for a smoke.</b>

07:31.871 --> 07:32.951
<b>Urk!</b>

07:32.951 --> 07:36.711
<b>Sorry, Yamada-san, 
I know I shouldn't be here!</b>

07:36.711 --> 07:40.131
<b>I'm just taking advantage of 
Tayama-san's gracious offer!</b>

07:40.131 --> 07:42.591
<b>She didn't do anything wrong!</b>

07:43.671 --> 07:45.421
<b>So, uh...</b>

07:46.921 --> 07:50.891
<b>It's all right, Sasaki-san. 
I knew that already.</b>

07:51.931 --> 07:54.351
<b>Tayama-chan told me.</b>

07:54.351 --> 07:57.061
<b>Oh, she did?</b>

07:57.311 --> 07:59.811
<b>You two must be good friends.</b>

08:02.561 --> 08:03.821
<b>Sa-slow-ki.</b>

08:03.901 --> 08:05.821
<b>Sa-slow-ki</b>

08:04.691 --> 08:05.571
<b>Huh?</b>

08:05.571 --> 08:07.651
<b>Yes, we're very close!</b>

08:07.651 --> 08:09.071
<b>I knew it.</b>

08:09.361 --> 08:12.321
<b>You must have a lot in common.</b>

08:12.321 --> 08:17.831
<b>You're both very attentive and thoughtful.</b>

08:20.831 --> 08:23.671
<b>Oh, right. Uh, Yamada-san?</b>

08:23.671 --> 08:24.671
<b>Yes?</b>

08:24.671 --> 08:26.091
<b>Uh...</b>

08:26.801 --> 08:29.591
<b>Is Tayama-san doing okay?</b>

08:30.881 --> 08:33.601
<b>She is, why?</b>

08:34.051 --> 08:36.771
<b>Is this about the complaint?</b>

08:36.771 --> 08:43.361
<b>Yeah. She told me a little about it.</b>

08:43.771 --> 08:46.111
<b>I was worried if she'd be okay.</b>

08:48.111 --> 08:49.741
<b>She's fine.</b>

08:50.071 --> 08:53.371
<b>I was worried, too, 
but you know what she said?</b>

08:53.621 --> 08:56.451
<b>That she forgot all about it after 
eating some ramen and going to sleep.</b>

08:57.951 --> 09:00.621
<b>Is that so? Glad to hear it.</b>

09:01.081 --> 09:06.171
<b>I hope you'll let her vent to you again.</b>

09:06.171 --> 09:07.881
<b>Oh, but...</b>

09:08.211 --> 09:13.761
<b>If she's already put it behind her, 
I don't think I should bring it up again.</b>

09:14.641 --> 09:18.271
<b>It doesn't have to be 
about this particular matter.</b>

09:18.271 --> 09:23.771
<b>Cold</b>

09:18.271 --> 09:23.771
<b>Cold</b>

09:18.271 --> 09:23.771
<b>Cold</b>

09:18.641 --> 09:23.191
<b>I'll let her know that you were 
concerned about her.</b>

09:23.771 --> 09:28.281
<b>What? A-Are you sure? 
Wouldn't I be overstepping?</b>

09:28.611 --> 09:32.031
<b>Overstepping? When she was 
the one who came to you about it?</b>

09:32.781 --> 09:34.281
<b>It's a bit late for that now.</b>

09:34.571 --> 09:38.161
<b>Oh, true.</b>

09:39.871 --> 09:41.911
<b>By the way, Yamada-san.</b>

09:42.291 --> 09:44.921
<b>Thank you for the other day.</b>

09:46.001 --> 09:47.791
<b>I heard from Tayama-san.</b>

09:48.461 --> 09:52.921
<b>She told me you were worried 
I seemed down in the dumps.</b>

09:53.431 --> 09:59.101
<b>I never got the chance to thank you, as 
I didn't want to bother you while working.</b>

09:59.101 --> 10:00.561
<b>Oh, that's fine.</b>

10:03.561 --> 10:10.071
<b>Work had me down, so I really appreciated 
having someone look out for me.</b>

10:12.571 --> 10:18.081
<b>I'm glad. As long as 
I wasn't overstepping...</b>

10:18.411 --> 10:21.701
<b>Wait, overstepping?</b>

10:22.701 --> 10:25.211
<b>I suppose it's a bit late for that, too.</b>

10:27.251 --> 10:29.841
<b>That would be the natural conclusion.</b>

10:32.591 --> 10:35.971
<b>Oh, I'm sorry for keeping you.</b>

10:35.971 --> 10:37.091
<b>Not at all.</b>

10:37.391 --> 10:42.601
<b>I've been wanting to speak with you like 
Tayama-chan, so I'm glad I got the chance.</b>

10:44.641 --> 10:49.191
<b>She's not here right now, 
but feel free to have a smoke.</b>

10:49.191 --> 10:51.111
<b>Thank you.</b>

10:52.731 --> 10:56.111
<b>Actually, I'll refrain today.</b>

10:56.111 --> 10:58.871
<b>I wouldn't want to get 
the smell of smoke on you.</b>

11:00.031 --> 11:02.581
<b>Sorry to take up your valuable break time.</b>

11:03.251 --> 11:04.041
<b>See you.</b>

11:09.671 --> 11:10.841
<b>Sasaki-san.</b>

11:10.841 --> 11:11.801
<b>Yes?</b>

11:24.391 --> 11:27.811
<b>You've had a petal 
in your hair this whole time.</b>

11:29.271 --> 11:31.481
<b>What? The whole time?</b>

11:31.481 --> 11:32.441
<b>Yeah.</b>

11:32.441 --> 11:35.611
<b>A geezer with a flower...</b>

11:36.531 --> 11:37.901
<b>It was so cute,</b>

11:37.901 --> 11:39.781
<b>I couldn't bring myself to tell you.</b>

11:40.071 --> 11:41.321
<b>Sorry about that.</b>

11:42.781 --> 11:45.911
<b>No, uh, thank you.</b>

11:53.381 --> 11:55.671
<b><i>I didn't expect that from Yamada-san.</i></b>

11:56.801 --> 11:59.091
<b><i>She's got a playful side, too, huh?</i></b>

12:22.071 --> 12:24.701
<b><i>Sasaki-san's so dense,</i></b>

12:29.711 --> 12:30.961
<b><i>it's almost funny.</i></b>

12:32.291 --> 12:35.921
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

12:36.421 --> 12:40.051
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

12:40.761 --> 12:44.011
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
